name: Frog Feast (itch)
description:
Welcome to Frog Feast, the ultimate game of quick reflexes and fruity goodness!

In this addictive game, you control a hungry frog on a mission to eat every fruit in sight. Use your mouse to lead the frog through each level, avoiding dangerous saws that threaten to end your journey.

As you progress through each level, the challenge intensifies with increasing difficulty. The cool music and colorful graphics will immerse you in the game, making it hard to put down.

But beware, this seemingly simple game is anything but easy! You'll need to stay sharp and quick on your feet to beat the game and claim the title of top frog.

And don't worry, we've got you covered - you can save your progress and track your highest level ever reached, so you can always come back and beat your own record.

Get ready for a wild ride of fruit-filled fun and challenging obstacles in Frog Feast. Are you up for the challenge?
